title: A Review of Episode 1220 Joey Diaz
description:
Joey Diaz is the funniest man on the planet! I’ve seen him live many times and when Rogan says he’s that good HE’S CORRECT! If you ever get the chance to see him or if he comes to your city go out of your way to watch this amazing man do his stand-up. We’re honored to have this unique individual on the planet. This is Rogan’s Christmas eve podcast with his closest friend. Such a great conversation to review. Make sure to check it out!

Enjoy my review folks!
